title: Modern Downtown Condo with City Views
description: Stunning modern condo in the heart of downtown San Francisco featuring floor-to-ceiling windows with breathtaking city views. This beautifully designed unit offers an open-concept living space with hardwood floors throughout, a gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances and quartz countertops, and a spacious master suite with walk-in closet. Building amenities include a rooftop deck, fitness center, and concierge services. Perfect for urban professionals seeking luxury living with easy access to public transportation, fine dining, and cultural attractions.

title: Charming Victorian Single Family Home
description: Beautifully restored Victorian home combining historic charm with modern conveniences. This elegant property features original hardwood floors, crown molding, and period details throughout. The spacious layout includes a formal dining room, updated kitchen with granite countertops, and a cozy family room with fireplace. The master suite boasts a luxurious en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet. Outside, enjoy the mature landscaping, rose garden, and detached garage. Located in a quiet residential neighborhood with excellent schools nearby.

title: Luxury Penthouse with Bay Views
description: Exceptional penthouse offering unparalleled luxury and stunning panoramic views of the San Francisco Bay and Golden Gate Bridge. This architectural masterpiece features soaring ceilings, floor-to-ceiling windows, and premium finishes throughout. The gourmet kitchen includes top-of-the-line European appliances, custom cabinetry, and a large island perfect for entertaining. The master suite is a true retreat with a spa-like bathroom featuring a soaking tub and separate shower. Private elevator access and two assigned parking spaces complete this extraordinary offering.

title: Cozy Starter Home in Family Neighborhood
description: Perfect starter home for first-time buyers or investors looking for potential. This well-maintained property sits on a generous lot in a desirable family-friendly neighborhood. The home features a bright living room with large windows, updated kitchen with newer appliances, and comfortable bedrooms with good natural light. The backyard offers plenty of space for gardening, entertaining, or children to play. Located near good schools, parks, and shopping centers with easy access to public transportation.

title: Contemporary Townhouse with Garage
description: Stunning contemporary townhouse in a prime Palo Alto location featuring modern design and high-quality finishes. This three-story home offers an open-concept main level perfect for entertaining, with a sleek kitchen featuring quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. Each bedroom includes an en-suite bathroom for maximum privacy and convenience. The attached two-car garage provides secure parking and storage. The private patio is perfect for outdoor dining and relaxation. Walking distance to downtown shops, restaurants, and tech companies.

title: Spacious Family Home with Pool
description: Magnificent family estate offering luxury living and entertainment possibilities. This impressive two-story home features a grand foyer, formal living and dining rooms, and a spacious family room with built-in entertainment center. The gourmet kitchen boasts granite countertops, custom cabinetry, and a breakfast nook overlooking the backyard. The master suite includes a sitting area, walk-in closet, and spa-like bathroom. Outside, enjoy the resort-style backyard with swimming pool, spa, and covered patio perfect for hosting gatherings year-round.

title: Modern Loft in Arts District
description: Spectacular industrial loft in the vibrant SOMA Arts District featuring soaring 14-foot ceilings, exposed brick walls, and oversized windows that flood the space with natural light. This unique property combines urban sophistication with artistic flair, perfect for creative professionals. The open floor plan includes a modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances and a spacious bathroom with contemporary fixtures. Building amenities include a common rooftop deck with city views and secure entry. Walking distance to galleries, restaurants, and nightlife.

title: Suburban Ranch with Large Lot
description: Beautifully maintained single-story ranch home on a sprawling quarter-acre lot in desirable Fremont location. This well-designed home features an open living area with vaulted ceilings, updated kitchen with granite counters and stainless appliances, and comfortable bedrooms with ample closet space. The highlight is the expansive backyard with mature fruit trees, vegetable garden area, and plenty of room for RV parking or future additions. Excellent schools nearby and convenient access to Silicon Valley tech companies.

title: Historic Craftsman Bungalow
description: Meticulously preserved Craftsman bungalow showcasing exceptional period details and architectural integrity. This charming home features original hardwood floors, built-in cabinetry, decorative moldings, and a stunning stone fireplace in the living room. The updated kitchen seamlessly blends modern functionality with vintage charm, while the spacious bedrooms offer comfortable retreats. The mature landscaping includes established gardens and a charming front porch perfect for relaxing. Just minutes from downtown Santa Cruz and beautiful beaches.

title: New Construction Modern Farmhouse
description: Brand new modern farmhouse combining contemporary design with rustic charm in the heart of wine country. This stunning home features an open-concept floor plan with high ceilings, luxury vinyl plank flooring, and a gourmet kitchen with quartz countertops and professional-grade appliances. The master suite includes a walk-in closet and spa-inspired bathroom with soaking tub. Outside, enjoy the covered patio overlooking vineyard views and the beautifully landscaped yard. Energy-efficient construction with solar panels and smart home technology throughout.

title: Waterfront Cottage with Private Dock
description: Rare waterfront cottage offering direct bay access and breathtaking views of San Francisco skyline. This unique property features panoramic windows throughout, capturing stunning water views from every room. The open living area flows seamlessly to outdoor decks perfect for entertaining and enjoying spectacular sunsets. The private dock accommodates boats up to 35 feet, making this ideal for water enthusiasts. Recently updated with new flooring, paint, and fixtures while maintaining its charming coastal character. Truly a one-of-a-kind opportunity in prestigious Sausalito.

title: Mountain View Estate with Acreage
description: Magnificent estate on one full acre offering privacy, luxury, and stunning mountain views. This impressive Mediterranean-style home features soaring ceilings, elegant archways, and premium materials throughout. The gourmet kitchen includes professional appliances, butler's pantry, and breakfast nook. The master wing provides a private retreat with sitting room, walk-in closets, and luxurious bathroom with jetted tub. Additional highlights include a home office, wine cellar, and three-car garage. The grounds feature mature oak trees, formal gardens, swimming pool, and tennis court.
